        "subject": "LU-18449 llite: fix wrong VM_HUGEPAGE readahead check",
        "message": "LU-18449 llite: fix wrong VM_HUGEPAGE readahead check\n\nThe client should check whether the reading page is covered by a\nDLM extent lock only when index of the page is not current mmap\nreading one.\n\nOtherwise, it will cause sanityn/test_16a fsx testing failure.\nThis patch fixes it accordingly.\n\nFixes: e7d3f7c063 (\" LU-18449 llite: handle kernel readahead for VM_HUGEPAGE vma\")\nChange-Id: I9e37951831bc9d4da04730d1b0dbe2abfa652c9b\nSigned-off-by: Yingjin Qian <qian@ddn.com>\n"
      },
